Follow the next steps to run the sample on Tomcat 7.0

- Install Eclipse
- Run Eclipse
- Add m2eclipse plugin to Eclipse (maven)
- Add subclipse plugin to Eclipse (subversion)
- Download and unzip Tomcat 7
- In SVN add a new repository http://mybatis.googlecode.com/svn
- In SVN go to sub-projects/jpetstore-6/trunk/
- Mouse right click and select "Check out as Maven project"
- Go to projects. Right click on JPetStore project and select "run on server"
- Select Tomcat 7 Server and set your installation directory
- JPetStore home page should be shown